Enum UpgradeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UpgradeType>
      • bwapi.UpgradeType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<UpgradeType>

    public enum UpgradeType
extends Enum<UpgradeType>
    The upgrade type represents a passive upgrade that can be obtained with Unit.upgrade(bwapi.UpgradeType).

        public UnitType whatsRequired(int level)
